### **4. 30_ChartStreamBridge**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes numeric streams in a smooth, real-time chart designed for live data feeds.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# ChartStreamBridge - Live Data Plotter

ChartStreamBridge renders live data with scrollable, dynamic line charts great for metrics, monitoring, or experiments.

## Features
- Realtime line chart  
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Built with Matplotlib  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/30_ChartStreamBridge.git
cd 30_ChartStreamBridge
python visualize.py
